OL,4,Csigning Florian Wirtz
OL,6,FLiverpool FC have reached an agreement
OL,7,Fwith Bayer Leverkusen to sign
OL,8,Fattacking midfielder Florian Wirtz for
OL,9,Fa British transfer record fee of #116m.
OL,11,FIt is understood the deal is made up
OL,12,Fof an initial #100m plus #16m in
OL,13,Fperformance-related add ons.
OL,15,FIt is a massive statement of intent by
OL,16,Fthe Premier League champions signing
OL,17,Fthe 22-year-old Germany international
OL,18,Fwho is widely regarded as one of the
OL,19,Fbrightest and most exciting attacking
OL,20,Ftalents in world football.
