OL,3,CTen facts about record-breaking
OL,4,Csigning Florian Wirtz
OL,6,FHe will become the club's most
OL,7,Fexpensive player ever, overtaking
OL,8,Fstriker Darwin Nunez who has cost
OL,9,Faround #85m with all his add ons after
OL,10,Fsigning from Benfica in 2022.
OL,12,FThe Reds had two bids rejected, the
OL,13,Flast one of #113m which would have
OL,14,Fseen #100m paid up front with
OL,15,Fperformance-related add-ons, but have
OL,16,Ffinally got the deal over the line.
OL,18,FThe attacking midfielder will be
OL,19,FLiverpool's second signing of the
OL,20,Fsummer from German club Bayern
OL,21,FLeverkusen following Jeremie Frimpong.
