OL,4,Csigning Florian Wirtz
OL,6,FThe 24-year-old Netherlands
OL,7,Finternational joined for around #30m
OL,8,Fas a replacement for Trent Alexander-
OL,9,FArnold after his move to Real Madrid.
OL,11,FIt's stark contrast to last summer
OL,12,Fwhere Liverpool's only major addition
OL,13,Fto the squad was Italian Federico
OL,14,FChiesa from Juventus for a reported
OL,15,F#10m.
OL,17,FSo who is Florian Wirtz?
OL,19,FHere are 10 facts about Liverpool's
OL,20,Frecord breaking signing:
