OL,3,CTen facts about record-breaking
OL,4,Csigning Florian Wirtz
OL,6,F1. Came through the youth ranks at FC
OL,7,FCologne before being signed by Bayer
OL,8,FLeverkusen in 2020.
OL,10,F2. Became the youngest player to ever
OL,11,Fplay for Leverkusen in the league when
OL,12,Fhe made his debut aged 17 years and 15
OL,13,Fdays. Just 19 days later he became the
OL,14,Fyoungest goalscorer in the history of
OL,15,FGermany's Bundesliga when he scored
OL,16,Fagainst Bayern Munich.
