OL,3,CTen facts about record-breaking
OL,4,Csigning Florian Wirtz
OL,6,F3. Working under former Liverpool
OL,7,Fmidfielder Xavi Alonso, Wirtz had a
OL,8,Fstandout year in 2023/24 where he was
OL,9,Fvoted Bundesliga player of the season
OL,10,Fafter doing the double and winning
OL,11,Fboth the German league and cup.
OL,13,F4. Idol is Lionel Messi and his former
OL,14,Fhead coach Alonso has even compared
OL,15,Fthe young German's playing style to
OL,16,Fthe legendary Argentina forward.
