OL,3,CTen facts about record-breaking
OL,4,Csigning Florian Wirtz
OL,6,F5. On the international stage Wirtz
OL,7,Fscored twice in the semi finals of the
OL,8,FUnder 21s European Championships as
OL,9,FGermany went all the way to win the
OL,10,Ftournament.
OL,12,F6. His goal against Scotland in the
OL,13,Fopening game of Euro 2024 saw him
OL,14,Fbecome the youngest person to score
OL,15,Ffor Germany at a Euros. He was 21
OL,16,Fyears and 42 days.
