OL,3,CTen facts about record-breaking
OL,4,Csigning Florian Wirtz
OL,6,F7. He's the second fastest goalscorer
OL,7,Fin international football history,
OL,8,Fscoring his first goal for his country
OL,9,Fjust seven seconds into their friendly
OL,10,Fwith France in March 2024.
OL,12,F8. He has a big family! He's the
OL,13,Fyoungest of ten children and has five
OL,14,Fsisters and four brothers.
OL,16,F9. Football runs in his family, his
OL,17,Fdad Hans-Joachim is the chairman of
OL,18,Flocal club SV Grun-Weiss Brauweiler
OL,19,Fand his older sister Juliane is also a
OL,20,Fprofessional playing in the Women's
OL,21,FBundesliga for Werder Bremen.
